title: 12/02/20 HOUR 3- Gerry Dulac
itunes:title: 12/02/20 HOUR 3- Gerry Dulac
description:
Gerry Dulac tells Dan that the Ravens have not changed their approach to the Steelers game with all of their back ups in the lineup today. Gerry says that RG III and the Ravens had a good game against the Steelers during the last game of the season last year.
